4_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2195,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":83712,"username":"ht","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ht","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e94/de24/83712_mini.png?m=1446086602","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e94/de24/83712_normal.png?m=1446086602","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e94/de24/83712_large.png?m=1446086602","created":1416905534,"last_modified":1446086602},"last_reply_by":"christin","last_touched":1655949456,"title":"Apple watch 的锻炼圆环时间很难记入","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/861540","created":1655946353,"deleted":0,"content":"18 年开始用 Apple Watch ，当时锻炼圆环只是日常走动上下楼梯都能准确记入进去，一天下来不用特意进行体能训练，锻炼圆环也能有个十几分钟。然而当下我即便是户外步行 10 分钟，要么计入 0 分钟，要么计入 1 分钟，一天下来的日常活动锻炼圆环就是铁打不动的 4 分钟。\r\n\r\n请问是 Apple 的计算逻辑优化了还是对个人用户的运动习惯给予不同的计入标准？例如运动量大的，日常活动的锻炼时间忽略不计。\r\n\r\n告诉我，我不是一个人。😂","content_rendered":"<p>18 年开始用 Apple Watch ，当时锻炼圆环只是日常走动上下楼梯都能准确记入进去，一天下来不用特意进行体能训练，锻炼圆环也能有个十几分钟。然而当下我即便是户外步行 10 分钟，要么计入 0 分钟，要么计入 1 分钟，一天下来的日常活动锻炼圆环就是铁打不动的 4 分钟。</p>\n<p>请问是 Apple 的计算逻辑优化了还是对个人用户的运动习惯给予不同的计入标准？例如运动量大的，日常活动的锻炼时间忽略不计。</p>\n<p>告诉我，我不是一个人。😂</p>\n","last_modified":1655946353,"replies":15,"id":861540},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":186430,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3500,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":541267,"username":"xwayway","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xwayway","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/grav